OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'World-leading' Down's     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsyndrome bill clears first 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fhurdle in Parliament       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Plans to ensure people with Down's     
OL,6, syndrome get lifelong care have passed 
OL,7, the first hurdle on the way to being   
OL,8, law in England.                        
OL,10,FMP Liam Fox said his bill was needed   
OL,11,Fnow because people with Down's syndrome
OL,12,Fare starting to outlive their parents. 
OL,14,FThe Tory former minister said it would 
OL,15,F"lighten the burden" on parents who    
OL,16,Fworried about what would happen to     
OL,17,Ftheir children after they died.        
OL,19,FThe legislation has government support 
OL,20,Fand is therefore likely to become law. 
